see what happens.

19:00.514 --> 19:02.016
Come on, Sam.

19:02.224 --> 19:03.726
Listen to your partner
for once.

19:09.774 --> 19:11.108
[ BREATHING SHARPLY ]

19:28.751 --> 19:30.127
DANIEL: Don't be scared.

19:30.252 --> 19:31.504
